Fluor Corporation Employee Statistics




School/University


Top Degrees


Also Worked at


Time at Fluor Corporation

























                                                The top most commonly attended alma maters among Fluor Corporation employees are Chapin High School, Midlands technical college, Certifications and Training, Corllins University, and Augusta Technical College.
                                            

                                                There's plenty to be said about the intellectual environment at Fluor Corporation based on trends in employee education. Overall, the most common educational background among employees at Fluor Corporation is high school graduate (20.78% of workers). When it come to academic achievement at Fluor Corporation, about 1.94% of employees hold a Bachelor of Arts degree while 7.48% have a Bachelor of Science.
                                            

                                                Other companies like Flour Corporation, Fluor Daniel Caribbean, Inc, KBR Inc, SecurAmerica LLC, and Orrefors Kosta Boda are popular choices for Fluor Corporation applicants.
                                            



























