11.04.2017


Article







Marathon Selects Fluor for Two Texas Refineries


Fluor Corporation was selected by a division of Marathon Petroleum Corporation to execute the engineering and procurement scope for a major reconfiguration at Marathon’s Galveston Bay and Texas City, Texas refineries.

read...









02.04.2017


Article







Fluor Completes Dow Chemical’s Ethylene Production Facility in Freeport on Schedule 


Fluor has finished the mechanical construction of The Dow Chemical Company’s new ethylene production facility in Freeport, Texas on schedule.

read...









23.03.2017


Article







Fluor’s Stork Awarded Five-Year Contract by Huntsman


Fluor announced that Stork, Fluor’s maintenance, modification and asset integrity segment, was awarded a five-year contract by Huntsman International, for maintenance and sustaining small capital projects at four of its differentiated chemicals manufacturing sites in Texas.

read...




























20.03.2017


Article







Yara Extends Global Alliance Framework Agreement with Fluor


Fluor announced that its global alliance framework agreement with Yara Belgium, European producer of ammonia and nitrate fertilizer, has been extended by three years and expanded to provide engineering, procurement and construction management services to support the client's glob...

read...









