Fluor Corporation - Wikipedia






















 







Fluor Corporation

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Fluor Corporation










Fluor headquarters in Irving, Texas



Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: FLR
